To compile
gcc -g BlockChain.c -lssl -lcrypto

Function descrpition

void addBlock(int);
Adds a singe block holding an iteger(users input) into the blockchain. 


void verifyChain();
Verifies if the chain has been tampered with.(Make's sure all the hash values match) 

void alterNthBlock(int, int);
Allows you to tamper with the blockchain.

void hackChain();
Fixes the hash values in the blockchain once it has been tampered with.  

void printBlock();
Prints the first block

void printAllBlocks();
Prints all blocks in the chain. 